{
  "stem": "26765.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then both my father and my Uncle Ludwig died within a few months-- my Uncle Ludwig actually within a few days after his dismissal from Sachsenhausen camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my father had a textile business which had been in the family for generations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather had the business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- we made suits and dresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we made the trousseau, embroidered the linen for the trousseau, the tablecloths, the towels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also made the down comforters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was quite a good sized store from what I hear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I'm not sure about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I also have some very nice memories of my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember sleeping in the bed with my mother-- probably it was after my father died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard a dog barking outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've always been-- as long as I can remember, I've been afraid of dogs-- maybe because of the police dogs that were prevalent in Germany at that time, and that, of course, I always saw in the concentration camps later.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for some reason, I was afraid of dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember my mother put her arm around me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And like a miracle, all of my fears disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was such a beautiful memory of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I also remember all of the songs that she sang.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother sang a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she sang a song which was popular in Germany in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was called, 'Ich tanze mit dir in den Himmel, in den siebenden Himmel der Liebe.' In English, the translation is, 'I danced with you into heaven, the seventh heaven of love.' And this song gives me a picture-- a beautiful picture of heaven-- as if it were a ballroom.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I've always loved dancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
